---
title: Garlic, Herb & Bacon Gnocchi Traybake with Pear Salad & Cheddar Cheese
description: Soft pillowy bundles of potato gnocchi, smothered in cheese and baked with bacon until deliciously golden and cheesy. Now, if that hasn’t got
your mouth watering, wait until you pull this dish of bubbling goodness from your oven in just 25 minutes.
